episodes.title: Vanished: Six Missouri Residents Connected to ‘Cosmic Cult,’ Investigators Reveal | Crime Alert 1...
episodes.description:
Authorities in Missouri are actively searching for a group of six individuals, including four adults and two children, who have been missing since July. New evidence suggests potential links to a cult known as the 'University of Cosmic Intelligence.'
